<title>bḥbk ạ̉nạ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ạ̉jyb mnyn ḥrwf tʿbr wmyn dạ qwlly yạrb yqdr yḥs by
 wsṭ ạlạ̉lm wsṭ ạlẓrwf wạ̉mạ ạ̉tnfḍ wạ̉ʿysẖ fy kẖwf tạkẖd ạ̹ydy
 ạlqrạr- ḥbk fy qlby hzny yạrb nfsy tḍmny wạ̉nʿs fy ḥḍnk
 kẖdny ḥnyny lnẓrtk bạrsm lqlby ḍḥktk lmạ ạ̉qwlk
 bạḥbk ạ̉nạ tkẖṭfny yạrby bạḥbk ạ̉nạ msẖ ʿạrf ạ̉kẖby
 2- ḥḍnt dmwʿy ḍḥkty fy ṣlạty ḥby ytḥky
 msẖtạq ạ̹lyk mlhwfẗ ʿyny tlmḥk tạkẖd ạ̹ydy blmstk kẖbyny fyk</lyrics>
